cat << EOF
Dialog lets you to present a variety of questions or display messages using
dialog boxes from a shell script (or any scripting language).
These types of dialog boxes are implemented: yes/no box, menu box, input box,
message box, text box, info box, guage box, checklist box, fileselection box,
and radiolist box.
